text: Jakub Čunta (born 28 August 1996) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for Šamorín as a left back, in II. Liga .Jakub Čunta novou posilou STK Fluminense Šamorín‚ stksamorin.sk, 30 January 2018 ==Club career== ===FK Senica=== Čunta made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for Senica on 30 May 2015 against ŽP Šport Podbrezová.SENICA VS.
